### Description

Provide a framework to make it easier to find a default network
interface.

New version of #6108 

Envisaged use:

NetworkInterface &net = NetworkInterface::get_default_instance();
net.connect();

// for advanced users:
WiFiInterface *wifi = net.wifiInterface();
if (wifi) {
    wifi->do_something_wifiy();
}

